name: Evan Silver
headline: Founder & CEO - Simplista
summary: Clean and complete item data is table stakes for an efficient retail operation, yet retailers and brands struggle to quickly and accurately exchange and transmit the hundreds of pieces of data required to sell a single product. Simplista provides real-time automated item setup, enabling brands to list their products into stores and ecommerce in hours (not weeks or months), and retailers to automatically capture brand changes as they happen. Equally important, our tech finds and fixes gaps and errors in the retailer’s back end, to ensure 100% accurate product information flows into every application that relies on item data. Simplista leverages AI, Computer Vision and Workflow automation to ensure speed to shelf and site, and proven revenue and gross margin gains for retailers and their brand partners.
